Teriyaki Salmon Burger

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

Description

Juicy salmon patty glazed with a sweet teriyaki sauce, served on a toasted bun with fresh toppings.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillet: 1 pound
  • panko breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1
  • green onion: 2, chopped
  • teriyaki sauce: 1/4 cup
  • burger buns: 4
  • sliced avocado: 1
  • sliced cucumber: 1
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
